{"data":[{"name":"53:1","price":"星¹にかけて（誓う）。それが、落ち（て消え）た時。²","arabic":"وَٱلنَّجۡمِ إِذَا هَوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4785,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　この「星」には、「徐々に下ったクルアーン*の啓示」との解釈もある（イブン・カスィール７：４４２参照）。 ２　この「誓い」については、整列者章１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-najmi idhā hawā ","translations":["By the star","when","it goes down","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-najmi","idhā","hawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2350],[2,2350,2980],[3,2980,3855]]}},{"name":"53:2","price":"あなた方の同胞（ムハンマド*）は（導きから）迷ったのでもなく、（信念を）誤ったのでもない。","arabic":"مَا ضَلَّ صَاحِبُكُمۡ وَمَا غَوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4786,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"mā ḍalla ṣāḥibukum wamā ghawā ","translations":["Not","has strayed","your companion","and not","has he erred","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","ḍalla","ṣāḥibukum","wamā","ghawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,1170],[3,1170,2600],[4,2600,3320],[5,3320,4125]]}},{"name":"53:3","price":"また、彼は私欲で語っているのでもない。","arabic":"وَمَا يَنطِقُ عَنِ ٱلۡهَوَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4787,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yanṭiqu ʿani al-hawā ","translations":["And not","he speaks","from","the desire","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yanṭiqu","ʿani","al-hawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,2560],[3,2560,2930],[4,2930,4025]]}},{"name":"53:4","price":"それ¹は、下される啓示以外の何ものでもないのだ。","arabic":"إِنۡ هُوَ إِلَّا وَحۡيٞ يُوحَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4788,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「それ」とは、クルアーン*とスンナ*のこと（ムヤッサル５２６頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"in huwa illā waḥyun yūḥā ","translations":["Not","it","(is) except","a revelation","revealed","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["in","huwa","illā","waḥyun","yūḥā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,470],[2,470,800],[3,800,1800],[4,1800,2550],[5,2550,4355]]}},{"name":"53:5","price":"強力な者（ジブリール*）が、彼（ムハンマド*）にそれを教えた。","arabic":"عَلَّمَهُۥ شَدِيدُ ٱلۡقُوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4789,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿallamahu shadīdu al-quwā ","translations":["Has taught him","the (one) mighty","(in) power","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿallamahu","shadīdu","al-quwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,2570],[3,2570,3445]]}},{"name":"53:6","price":"力を備えた者が。そして彼（ジブリール*）は真っ直ぐに立った、","arabic":"ذُو مِرَّةٖ فَٱسۡتَوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4790,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"dhū mirratin fa-is'tawā ","translations":["Possessor of soundness","Possessor of soundness","And he rose","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["dhū","mirratin","fa-is'tawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,560],[2,560,1950],[3,1950,3835]]}},{"name":"53:7","price":"空の向こうの最も高いところに¹。","arabic":"وَهُوَ بِٱلۡأُفُقِ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4791,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　預言者*が、ジブリール*をその本来の姿によって目にしたのは地上で一度（この時）、天界で一度（アーヤ*１３参照）だけだった。この時、ジブリール*は東方から出現して上方へと広がり、六百もの翼を広げつつ、西方の空までを覆ったのだという（アル＝クルトゥビー１７：８７参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wahuwa bil-ufuqi al-aʿlā ","translations":["While he","(was) in the horizon ","the highest","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wahuwa","bil-ufuqi","al-aʿlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,1850],[3,1850,3115]]}},{"name":"53:8","price":"それから（使徒*に）近づき、降りてきた。","arabic":"ثُمَّ دَنَا فَتَدَلَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4792,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma danā fatadallā ","translations":["Then","he approached","and came down","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","danā","fatadallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,2000],[3,2000,3475]]}},{"name":"53:9","price":"それで彼は（使徒*から）弓矢二本分か、それ以下（の近さ）であった。","arabic":"فَكَانَ قَابَ قَوۡسَيۡنِ أَوۡ أَدۡنَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4793,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fakāna qāba qawsayni aw adnā ","translations":["And was","(at) a distance","(of) two bow-(lengths)","or","nearer","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["fakāna","qāba","qawsayni","aw","adnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,1640],[3,1640,2850],[4,2850,3250],[5,3250,4235]]}},{"name":"53:10","price":"そしてかれ（アッラー*）は、かれが（ジブリール*に）啓示したことを、その僕に啓示した¹。","arabic":"فَأَوۡحَىٰٓ إِلَىٰ عَبۡدِهِۦ مَآ أَوۡحَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4794,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　同様の表現方法として、ター・ハー章３８「示されるもの」の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-awḥā ilā ʿabdihi mā awḥā ","translations":["So he revealed","to","His slave","what","he revealed","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-awḥā","ilā","ʿabdihi","mā","awḥā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2510],[2,2510,3160],[3,3160,4330],[4,4330,4510],[5,4510,5960],[6,5960,7045]]}},{"name":"53:11","price":"（使徒*の）その心は、彼が目の当たりにしたことについて、嘘をついたのではない。","arabic":"مَا كَذَبَ ٱلۡفُؤَادُ مَا رَأَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4795,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"mā kadhaba al-fuādu mā raā ","translations":["Not","lied","the heart","what","it saw","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","kadhaba","al-fuādu","mā","raā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,480],[2,480,1150],[3,1150,2370],[4,2370,2830],[5,2830,3565]]}},{"name":"53:12","price":"一体あなた方は、彼が見たことについて議論するというのか？","arabic":"أَفَتُمَٰرُونَهُۥ عَلَىٰ مَا يَرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4796,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"afatumārūnahu ʿalā mā yarā ","translations":["Then will you dispute with him","about","what","he saw","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["afatumārūnahu","ʿalā","mā","yarā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2320],[2,2320,3100],[3,3100,3570],[4,3570,4875]]}},{"name":"53:13","price":"彼（使徒*）は確かに、彼（ジブリール*）をもう一度、目にした。¹","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ رَءَاهُ نَزۡلَةً أُخۡرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4797,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　これは、預言者*が夜の旅（夜の旅章１とその訳注を参照）で昇天した際、ジブリール*をその本来の姿で二度目に目にした時のこととされる（イブン・カスィール７：４５１参照）。アーヤ*７の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walaqad raāhu nazlatan ukh'rā ","translations":["And certainly","he saw him","(in) descent","another","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["walaqad","raāhu","nazlatan","ukh'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1810],[3,1810,2950],[4,2950,4395]]}},{"name":"53:14","price":"最果てのスィドラ¹のもとで。","arabic":"عِندَ سِدۡرَةِ ٱلۡمُنتَهَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4798,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　天の第七層にある木で、地上から昇天した者はそこから先には進めない（ムヤッサル５２６頁参照）。 「スィドラ」については、サバア章１６「スィドル（スィドラの複数形）」の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿinda sid'rati al-muntahā ","translations":["Near","(the) Lote Tree","(of) the utmost boundary","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿinda","sid'rati","al-muntahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,2410],[3,2410,4665]]}},{"name":"53:15","price":"そこには、（敬虔な*者たちの）住処としての楽園がある。","arabic":"عِندَهَا جَنَّةُ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4799,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿindahā jannatu al-mawā ","translations":["Near it","(is the) Garden","(of) Abode","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿindahā","jannatu","al-mawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1930],[2,1930,3670],[3,3670,4965]]}},{"name":"53:16","price":"覆うものが、スィドラを覆っている時（、使徒*は見たのだ）。¹","arabic":"إِذۡ يَغۡشَى ٱلسِّدۡرَةَ مَا يَغۡشَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4800,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　同様の表現法として、ター・ハー章３８「示されるもの」の訳注も参照。「最果てのスィドラ」は、天使*たちと主*の御光、様々な色のものによって覆われているという（イブン・カスィール７：４５４参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"idh yaghshā al-sid'rata mā yaghshā ","translations":["When","covered","the Lote Tree","what","covers","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["idh","yaghshā","al-sid'rata","mā","yaghshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,490],[2,490,1090],[3,1090,2330],[4,2330,2780],[5,2780,3835]]}},{"name":"53:17","price":"（使徒*の）その目は、（彼が見ることを命じられたものから、）逸れることも、超えることもなかった。","arabic":"مَا زَاغَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ وَمَا طَغَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4801,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"mā zāgha al-baṣaru wamā ṭaghā ","translations":["Not","swerved","the sight","and not","it transgressed","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","zāgha","al-baṣaru","wamā","ṭaghā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1220],[3,1220,2150],[4,2150,2630],[5,2630,4275]]}},{"name":"53:18","price":"彼は確かに、彼の主*の最も偉大な御徴の一部¹を、目にしたのである。","arabic":"لَقَدۡ رَأَىٰ مِنۡ ءَايَٰتِ رَبِّهِ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4802,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「最も偉大な御徴」とは、天国と地獄などを始めとした、アッラー*の御力と偉大さを示す根拠の数々のこと（ムヤッサル５２６頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"laqad raā min āyāti rabbihi al-kub'rā ","translations":["Certainly","he saw","of","(the) Signs","(of) his Lord","the Greatest","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["laqad","raā","min","āyāti","rabbihi","al-kub'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1390],[3,1390,1830],[4,1830,3160],[5,3160,3980],[6,3980,5725]]}},{"name":"53:19","price":"（シルク*の徒よ、）言ってみよ、アッ＝ラートとアル＝ウッザー¹について、","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱللَّٰتَ وَٱلۡعُزَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4803,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　アーヤ２０の「マナート」も含めたこれら三つは、当時アラブ人の間で有名かつ偉大視 されていた偶像の名（アッ＝シャウカーニー５：１４２参照）。高壁章１８０の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"afara-aytumu al-lāta wal-ʿuzā ","translations":["So have you seen","the Lat","and the Uzza","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["afara-aytumu","al-lāta","wal-ʿuzā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1630],[2,1630,2720],[3,2720,4195]]}},{"name":"53:20","price":"また、別の三番目、マナートについて（、それらが害する力や益する力を有しているのかを）。","arabic":"وَمَنَوٰةَ ٱلثَّالِثَةَ ٱلۡأُخۡرَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4804,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamanata al-thālithata al-ukh'rā ","translations":["And Manat","the third","the other","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["wamanata","al-thālithata","al-ukh'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2600],[3,2600,4525]]}},{"name":"53:21","price":"一体、あなた方には息子があり、かれ（アッラー*）には娘があるというのか？¹","arabic":"أَلَكُمُ ٱلذَّكَرُ وَلَهُ ٱلۡأُنثَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4805,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　彼ら自身、娘を授かることを嫌っていたにも関わらず、天使*たちを「アッラー*の娘」と呼んだ（蜜蜂章５７－５９とその訳注を参照）り、あるいはアーヤ*１９－２０で言及されている偶像に女性の名前をつけたりしていたことを指している、とされる（前掲書５：１４３参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alakumu al-dhakaru walahu al-unthā ","translations":["Is for you","the male","and for Him","the female","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["alakumu","al-dhakaru","walahu","al-unthā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,1910],[3,1910,2590],[4,2590,4775]]}},{"name":"53:22","price":"だとしたら、それは不当な配分である。","arabic":"تِلۡكَ إِذٗا قِسۡمَةٞ ضِيزَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4806,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"til'ka idhan qis'matun ḍīzā ","translations":["This","then","(is) a division","unfair","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["til'ka","idhan","qis'matun","ḍīzā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,2180],[3,2180,4430],[4,4430,5565]]}},{"name":"53:23","price":"それらは、あなた方と、あなた方の先祖が名付けた名前¹に過ぎない。アッラー*はそれら（の崇拝*）に、いかなる（正当な）根拠も下されなかったのだ。彼らは憶測と、自分たちが欲するものに従っている外ならない。彼らのもとには、彼らの主*からの導きが、確かに到来したのである。","arabic":"إِنۡ هِيَ إِلَّآ أَسۡمَآءٞ سَمَّيۡتُمُوهَآ أَنتُمۡ وَءَابَآؤُكُم مَّآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ بِهَا مِن سُلۡطَٰنٍۚ إِن يَتَّبِعُونَ إِلَّا ٱلظَّنَّ وَمَا تَهۡوَى ٱلۡأَنفُسُۖ وَلَقَدۡ جَآءَهُم مِّن رَّبِّهِمُ ٱلۡهُدَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4807,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「・・・名前」については、高壁章７１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"in hiya illā asmāon sammaytumūhā antum waābāukum mā anzala al-lahu bihā min sul'ṭānin in yattabiʿūna illā al-ẓana wamā tahwā al-anfusu walaqad jāahum min rabbihimu al-hudā ","translations":["Not","they","(are) except","names","you have named them","you","and your forefathers","not","has Allah sent down","has Allah sent down","for it","any","authority","Not","they follow","except","assumption","and what","desire","the(ir) souls","And certainly","has come to them","from","their Lord","the guidance","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["in","hiya","illā","asmāon","sammaytumūhā","antum","waābāukum","mā","anzala","al-lahu","bihā","min","sul'ṭānin","in","yattabiʿūna","illā","al-ẓana","wamā","tahwā","al-anfusu","walaqad","jāahum","min","rabbihimu","al-hudā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,930],[3,930,3080],[4,3080,6460],[5,6460,9370],[6,9370,14280],[7,14280,15980],[8,15980,19500],[9,19500,21410],[10,21410,22810],[11,22810,23910],[12,23910,24560],[13,24560,24920],[14,24920,25760],[15,25760,29440],[16,29440,30390],[17,30390,31870],[18,31870,32570],[19,32570,34170],[20,34170,34810],[21,34810,35510],[22,35510,37820],[23,37820,39200],[24,39200,42030],[25,42030,43140],[26,43140,44520],[27,44520,45645]]}},{"name":"53:24","price":"いや、一体、人間には（それらの偶像から、）望み通りのもの¹があるというのか？","arabic":"أَمۡ لِلۡإِنسَٰنِ مَا تَمَنَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4808,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　それらのものに対する、執り成しのこと（ムヤッサル５２６頁参照）。 集団章３とその訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"am lil'insāni mā tamannā ","translations":["Or","(is) for man","what","he wishes","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["am","lil'insāni","mā","tamannā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,2850],[3,2850,3250],[4,3250,5335]]}},{"name":"53:25","price":"アッラー*にこそ、最後のもの（来世）と最初のもの（現世）が属するというのに。","arabic":"فَلِلَّهِ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةُ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4809,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"falillahi al-ākhiratu wal-ūlā ","translations":["But for Allah","(is) the last","and the first","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["falillahi","al-ākhiratu","wal-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1330],[2,1330,2790],[3,2790,4145]]}},{"name":"53:26","price":"一体、諸天にいるどれだけ多くの天使*の執り成しが、少しも役に立たないことであろうか。アッラー*が、かれがお望みにある者に（執り成しの）許可を授けられ、（執り成しを受ける者に対し、）ご満足する後でなければ。¹","arabic":"۞ وَكَم مِّن مَّلَكٖ فِي ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ لَا تُغۡنِي شَفَٰعَتُهُمۡ شَيۡـًٔا إِلَّا مِنۢ بَعۡدِ أَن يَأۡذَنَ ٱللَّهُ لِمَن يَشَآءُ وَيَرۡضَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4810,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　復活の日*の「執り成し」については雌牛章４８，マルヤム*章８７，ター・ハー章１０９とその訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wakam min malakin fī al-samāwāti lā tugh'nī shafāʿatuhum shayan illā min baʿdi an yadhana al-lahu liman yashāu wayarḍā ","translations":["And how many","of","(the) Angels","in","the heavens","not","will avail","their intercession","anything","except","after","after","[that]","Allah has given permission","Allah has given permission","for whom","He wills","and approves","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["wakam","min","malakin","fī","al-samāwāti","lā","tugh'nī","shafāʿatuhum","shayan","illā","min","baʿdi","an","yadhana","al-lahu","liman","yashāu","wayarḍā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,1590],[3,1590,3940],[4,3940,4260],[5,4260,5940],[6,5940,6350],[7,6350,7190],[8,7190,8850],[9,8850,10480],[10,10480,10890],[11,10890,11790],[12,11790,13390],[13,13390,14340],[14,14340,15330],[15,15330,16620],[16,16620,17280],[17,17280,17580],[18,17580,18250],[19,18250,19010],[20,19010,20100],[21,20100,20470],[22,20470,21130],[23,21130,23490],[24,23490,24785]]}},{"name":"53:27","price":"本当に、来世を信じない者たちこそが、天使たちを女性の名で名付ける¹のである。","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ لَا يُؤۡمِنُونَ بِٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ لَيُسَمُّونَ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةَ تَسۡمِيَةَ ٱلۡأُنثَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4811,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　アーヤ*２１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna alladhīna lā yu'minūna bil-ākhirati layusammūna al-malāikata tasmiyata al-unthā ","translations":["Indeed","those who","(do) not","believe","in the Hereafter","surely they name","the Angels","name(s)","(of) female","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","alladhīna","lā","yu'minūna","bil-ākhirati","layusammūna","al-malāikata","tasmiyata","al-unthā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1720],[2,1720,2850],[3,2850,3370],[4,3370,4740],[5,4740,6420],[6,6420,8710],[7,8710,11860],[8,11860,12920],[9,12920,15075]]}},{"name":"53:28","price":"彼らには、それについてわずかばかりの知識もないというのに。彼らは憶測に従っているに外ならない。実に、憶測は真理¹に対して何の役にも立たないのだが。","arabic":"وَمَا لَهُم بِهِۦ مِنۡ عِلۡمٍۖ إِن يَتَّبِعُونَ إِلَّا ٱلظَّنَّۖ وَإِنَّ ٱلظَّنَّ لَا يُغۡنِي مِنَ ٱلۡحَقِّ شَيۡـٔٗا","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4812,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　この「真理」は、知識、あるいは懲罰のことを指す（アル＝バガウィー４：３１０参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā lahum bihi min ʿil'min in yattabiʿūna illā al-ẓana wa-inna al-ẓana lā yugh'nī mina al-ḥaqi shayan ","translations":["And not","for them","about it","any","knowledge","Not","they follow","but","assumption","And indeed","the assumption","(does) not","avail","against","the truth","anything","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","lahum","bihi","min","ʿil'min","in","yattabiʿūna","illā","al-ẓana","wa-inna","al-ẓana","lā","yugh'nī","mina","al-ḥaqi","shayan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,670],[2,670,2209],[3,2209,2920],[4,2920,3350],[5,3350,4520],[6,4520,5740],[7,5740,7240],[8,7240,7870],[9,7870,9650],[10,9650,11000],[11,11000,12350],[12,12350,12820],[13,12820,13730],[14,13730,14170],[15,14170,15090],[16,15090,16145]]}},{"name":"53:29","price":"ならば（使徒*よ）、われら*の教訓（クルアーン*）から背を向け、現世しか欲することがなかった者から、背き去れ¹。","arabic":"فَأَعۡرِضۡ عَن مَّن تَوَلَّىٰ عَن ذِكۡرِنَا وَلَمۡ يُرِدۡ إِلَّا ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4813,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　撒き散らすもの章５４の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-aʿriḍ ʿan man tawallā ʿan dhik'rinā walam yurid illā al-ḥayata al-dun'yā ","translations":["So turn away","from","(him) who","turns away","from","Our Reminder","and not","he desires","except","the life","(of) the world","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-aʿriḍ","ʿan","man","tawallā","ʿan","dhik'rinā","walam","yurid","illā","al-ḥayata","al-dun'yā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,1370],[3,1370,2900],[4,2900,4050],[5,4050,5080],[6,5080,6190],[7,6190,6870],[8,6870,7560],[9,7560,8160],[10,8160,9310],[11,9310,10535]]}},{"name":"53:30","price":"それが、彼らの知識の限界¹。本当にあなたの主*こそは、かれの道から迷う者を最もよくご存知のお方であり、かれこそは導かれた者を最もよくご存知なのだから。","arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ مَبۡلَغُهُم مِّنَ ٱلۡعِلۡمِۚ إِنَّ رَبَّكَ هُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَن ضَلَّ عَن سَبِيلِهِۦ وَهُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَنِ ٱهۡتَدَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4814,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　来世よりも現世を優先させたという、彼らの知識の所産と理性に対する、蔑（さげす）みの表現（前掲書、同頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"dhālika mablaghuhum mina al-ʿil'mi inna rabbaka huwa aʿlamu biman ḍalla ʿan sabīlihi wahuwa aʿlamu bimani ih'tadā ","translations":["That","(is) their sum","of","knowledge","Indeed","your Lord","(is) He (Who)","knows best","(he) who","strays","from","His Path","and He","knows best","(he) who","is guided","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["dhālika","mablaghuhum","mina","al-ʿil'mi","inna","rabbaka","huwa","aʿlamu","biman","ḍalla","ʿan","sabīlihi","wahuwa","aʿlamu","bimani","ih'tadā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,2180],[3,2180,3410],[4,3410,4700],[5,4700,5690],[6,5690,6640],[7,6640,6960],[8,6960,7980],[9,7980,9200],[10,9200,9850],[11,9850,10790],[12,10790,12200],[13,12200,12880],[14,12880,13830],[15,13830,14510],[16,14510,15565]]}},{"name":"53:31","price":"アッラー*にこそ、諸天にあるものと大地にあるものは属する。かくして、かれは悪い行いだった者たちを彼らが行ったものによって報われ、善を尽くした者¹たちを最善のもの（天国）で報われる。","arabic":"وَلِلَّهِ مَا فِي ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَمَا فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ لِيَجۡزِيَ ٱلَّذِينَ أَسَٰٓـُٔواْ بِمَا عَمِلُواْ وَيَجۡزِيَ ٱلَّذِينَ أَحۡسَنُواْ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَى","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4815,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　蜜蜂章１２８「善を尽くす者」についての訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walillahi mā fī al-samāwāti wamā fī al-arḍi liyajziya alladhīna asāū bimā ʿamilū wayajziya alladhīna aḥsanū bil-ḥus'nā ","translations":["And for Allah","(is) whatever","(is) in","the heavens","and whatever","(is) in","the earth","that He may recompense","those who","do evil","with what","they have done","and recompense","those who","do good","with the best","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["walillahi","mā","fī","al-samāwāti","wamā","fī","al-arḍi","liyajziya","alladhīna","asāū","bimā","ʿamilū","wayajziya","alladhīna","aḥsanū","bil-ḥus'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1450],[2,1450,1820],[3,1820,2040],[4,2040,3810],[5,3810,4400],[6,4400,4650],[7,4650,5620],[8,5620,6710],[9,6710,7850],[10,7850,10859],[11,10859,11549],[12,11549,12569],[13,12569,13599],[14,13599,14699],[15,14699,15899],[16,15899,17414]]}},{"name":"53:32","price":"些細なもの¹は別として、罪の内の大きなもの（大罪*）と醜行²を避ける者たちを（、最善のもので報われる）。実にあなたの主*は、赦しの念の深いお方なのだから。かれは、あなた方（の父アーダム*）を大地からお創りになった時、そしてあなた方が自分たちの母親のお腹で胎児だった時（から）、あなた方について最もよくご存知なのだぞ。ならば、自分自身を（罪から）潔白であると主張してはならない。かれは敬虔*である者を、最もよくご存知なのだ。","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ يَجۡتَنِبُونَ كَبَٰٓئِرَ ٱلۡإِثۡمِ وَٱلۡفَوَٰحِشَ إِلَّا ٱللَّمَمَۚ إِنَّ رَبَّكَ وَٰسِعُ ٱلۡمَغۡفِرَةِۚ هُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِكُمۡ إِذۡ أَنشَأَكُم مِّنَ ٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَإِذۡ أَنتُمۡ أَجِنَّةٞ فِي بُطُونِ أُمَّهَٰتِكُمۡۖ فَلَا تُزَكُّوٓاْ أَنفُسَكُمۡۖ هُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَنِ ٱتَّقَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4816,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　「些細なもの」とは、本人を害しない程度の小さな罪、あるいは、稀（まれ）に犯してしまう小さな罪のこと。これらの行為は、義務（ぎむ）行為を行い、禁じられた物事を回避（かいひ）している限り、アッラー*がお赦し下さる（ムヤッサル５２７頁参照）。 ２　「醜行」については、蜜蜂章９０の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna yajtanibūna kabāira al-ith'mi wal-fawāḥisha illā al-lamama inna rabbaka wāsiʿu al-maghfirati huwa aʿlamu bikum idh ansha-akum mina al-arḍi wa-idh antum ajinnatun fī buṭūni ummahātikum falā tuzakkū anfusakum huwa aʿlamu bimani ittaqā ","translations":["Those who","avoid","great","sins","and the immoralities","except","the small faults","indeed","your Lord","(is) vast","(in) forgiveness","He","(is) most knowing about you","(is) most knowing about you","when","He produced you","from","the earth","and when","you (were)","fetuses","in","(the) wombs","(of) your mothers","So (do) not","ascribe purity","(to) yourselves","He","knows best","(he) who","fears","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","yajtanibūna","kabāira","al-ith'mi","wal-fawāḥisha","illā","al-lamama","inna","rabbaka","wāsiʿu","al-maghfirati","huwa","aʿlamu","bikum","idh","ansha-akum","mina","al-arḍi","wa-idh","antum","ajinnatun","fī","buṭūni","ummahātikum","falā","tuzakkū","anfusakum","huwa","aʿlamu","bimani","ittaqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1250],[2,1250,2800],[3,2800,5480],[4,5480,6470],[5,6470,8160],[6,8160,8690],[7,8690,10230],[8,10230,11420],[9,11420,12440],[10,12440,13250],[11,13250,15120],[12,15120,15460],[13,15460,16430],[14,16430,17120],[15,17120,17520],[16,17520,19290],[17,19290,20320],[18,20320,21340],[19,21340,21950],[20,21950,23550],[21,23550,25680],[22,25680,26520],[23,26520,27460],[24,27460,30550],[25,30550,31190],[26,31190,34260],[27,34260,36740],[28,36740,37080],[29,37080,38070],[30,38070,38740],[31,38740,40215]]}},{"name":"53:33","price":"（使徒*よ、）言ってみよ、（アッラー*への服従に）背き、¹","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي تَوَلَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4817,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　シルク*の徒の無知さについての描写がここで一旦終わり、ここからは彼らの内の特定の者が、その悪行と共に取り上げあれる。それが誰か、いかなる行いに関してか、という点については諸説ある（アル＝クルトゥビー１７：１１１参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"afara-ayta alladhī tawallā ","translations":["Did you see","the one who","turned away","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["afara-ayta","alladhī","tawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1280],[2,1280,2220],[3,2220,3475]]}},{"name":"53:34","price":"（自分の財産から）少しだけ与え、（吝嗇さゆえに、施しを）打ち切った者（について）。","arabic":"وَأَعۡطَىٰ قَلِيلٗا وَأَكۡدَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4818,"ju