たのか）？","arabic":"أَلَّا تَزِرُ وَازِرَةٞ وِزۡرَ أُخۡرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4822,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"allā taziru wāziratun wiz'ra ukh'rā ","translations":["That not","will bear","a bearer of burdens","(the) burden","(of) another","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["allā","taziru","wāziratun","wiz'ra","ukh'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1480],[3,1480,3510],[4,3510,4200],[5,4200,5645]]}},{"name":"53:39","price":"また人間には、自分が努力したもの（の報い）しかない、ということを？¹","arabic":"وَأَن لَّيۡسَ لِلۡإِنسَٰنِ إِلَّا مَا سَعَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4823,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"１　このことは、人が他人の努力から益を得る可能性を否定しているわけではなく（山章２１も参照）、人は自分自身の努力しか有してはおらず、他人の努力にまで立ち入ることは出来ないことを示している（アッ＝シャンキーティー７：４７０－４７１参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-an laysa lil'insāni illā mā saʿā ","translations":["And that","is not","for man","except","what","he strives (for)","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-an","laysa","lil'insāni","illā","mā","saʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1240],[3,1240,3650],[4,3650,4560],[5,4560,4950],[6,4950,5805]]}},{"name":"53:40","price":"また、その努力はやがて（来世で）目に見えるものとなり、","arabic":"وَأَنَّ سَعۡيَهُۥ سَوۡفَ يُرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4824,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-anna saʿyahu sawfa yurā ","translations":["And that","his striving","will soon","be seen","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-anna","saʿyahu","sawfa","yurā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,2420],[3,2420,3180],[4,3180,4395]]}},{"name":"53:41","price":"それから全き応報で、それを報われるのだということを？","arabic":"ثُمَّ يُجۡزَىٰهُ ٱلۡجَزَآءَ ٱلۡأَوۡفَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4825,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma yuj'zāhu al-jazāa al-awfā ","translations":["Then","he will be recompensed for it","the recompense","the 